####################
# 举报模块测试
####################

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 1. 注册普通测试用户
# @name reportUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "report_user_001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "举报测试用户",
  "email": "report_user@test.com",
  "phone": "13800000010",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}

### 2. 注册管理员测试用户
# @name reportAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "report_admin_001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "举报管理员",
  "email": "report_admin@test.com",
  "phone": "13800000011",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "admin"
}

### 手动设置token（从上面的注册响应中复制）
